{"tha-ap70:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap70:0.2":"Sakacintaniyavagga ","tha-ap70:0.3":"Ambadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap70:1.1":"“Anomadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap70:1.2":"nisinno pabbatantare; ","tha-ap70:1.3":"Mettaya aphari loke, ","tha-ap70:1.4":"appamane nirupadhi. ","tha-ap70:2.1":"Kapi aham tada asim, ","tha-ap70:2.2":"himavante naguttame; ","tha-ap70:2.3":"Disva anomadassim tam, ","tha-ap70:2.4":"buddhe cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap70:3.1":"Avidure himavantassa, ","tha-ap70:3.2":"ambasum phalino tada; ","tha-ap70:3.3":"Tato pakkam gahetvana, ","tha-ap70:3.4":"ambam samadhukam adam. ","tha-ap70:4.1":"Tam me buddho viyakasi, ","tha-ap70:4.2":"anomadassi mahamuni; ","tha-ap70:4.3":"Imina madhudanena, ","tha-ap70:4.4":"ambadanena cubhayam. ","tha-ap70:5.1":"Sattapannasakappamhi, ","tha-ap70:5.2":"devaloke ramissati; ","tha-ap70:5.3":"Avasesesu kappesu, ","tha-ap70:5.4":"vokinnam samsarissati. ","tha-ap70:6.1":"Khepetva papakam kammam, ","tha-ap70:6.2":"paripakkaya buddhiya; ","tha-ap70:6.3":"Vinipatamagantvana, ","tha-ap70:6.4":"kilese jhapayissati. ","tha-ap70:7.1":"Damena uttamenaham, ","tha-ap70:7.2":"damitomhi mahesina; ","tha-ap70:7.3":"Pattomhi acalam thanam, ","tha-ap70:7.4":"hitva jayaparajayam. ","tha-ap70:8.1":"Sattasattatikappasate, ","tha-ap70:8.2":"ambatthajasanamaka; ","tha-ap70:8.3":"Catuddasa te rajano, ","tha-ap70:8.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap70:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap70:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap70:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap70:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ambadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap70:11.1":"Ambadayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}